comments: Carter Jr. (ORL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Davis (LAL) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during Banchero's (ORL) driving shot attempt.
Suggs (ORL) cleanly dislodges the ball from Wood (LAL) and any further contact is incidental.
Davis (LAL) establishes himself in Carter Jr.'s (ORL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Carter Jr. (ORL) commits a take foul on Davis (LAL).
James (LAL) and Wagner (ORL) come together and marginal contact occurs as James releases away to receive the pass.
Davis (LAL) and Wagner (ORL) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs after the pick is set.
Davis (LAL) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Banchero (ORL) legally contests Wood's (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Wagner (ORL) and Davis (LAL) engage and disengage during the rebound.

Suggs (ORL) gains control of the loose ball and any contact with Prince (LAL) in pursuit of the loose ball is incidental.  Upon gaining possession of the ball, the Magic signal for and are awarded a timeout.
Davis (LAL) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during Suggs' (ORL) driving shot attempt.
Fultz (ORL) reaches in and initiates contact to Wood's (LAL) arm, affecting his SQBR when he has control of the ball.
Wagner (ORL) commits a take foul on Russell (LAL).
James (LAL) legally contests Wagner's (ORL) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is blocked and released.
Davis (LAL) legally contests Suggs' (ORL) jump shot attempt.
